	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm going to convert a Famicom Just Breed cart to English and I'm struggling to find a simple EKROM wiring sheet. From what I've gathered on here through random threads and in the wiki I've come up with this:<br /><br />CHR &amp; PRG:<br /><br />bent pin 1 to hole 30 <br />bent pin 2 to hole 24  <br />bent pin 24 to hole 31 <br />bent pin 30 to hole 1  <br />bent pin 31 to hole 2<br /><br />Does that seem right to anyone who has worked with the EKROM board before?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
